     D  @PTCOJ         S              1                                                             
     D  @PERRO         S              1                                                             
                                                                                                    
     D  ZXERRO         S              1                                                             
     D  ZXCAST         S                   LIKE(MOCAST)                                             
     D  ZXCASTA        S                   LIKE(MOCAST)                                             
     D  ZXCAST2        S                   LIKE(MOCAST)                                             
